title: Xi Jinping says Taiwan will 'surely' be reunified with China during symposium commemorating Mao
description: Chinese President Xi Jinping on his country's commitment to reunifying with Taiwan, vowing to prevent anyone from trying to split the two nations.

title: YouTuber helps Missouri police find remains of man missing since 2013
description: A tip from a YouTuber helped the Camden County Sheriff's Office in Missouri find the remains of man who had been missing since December 2013.

title: Former Baltimore prosecutor Marilyn Mosby faces possible disbarment amid ongoing legal battles
description: Former Baltimore City State's Attorney Marilyn Mosby faces potential professional discipline after allegedly misusing her finances during the COVID-19 pandemic.

title: Pregnant Texas teen Savanah Soto, baby and boyfriend shot to death
description: San Antonio Police are calling the death of pregnant 18-year-old Savanah Soto, her unborn baby and her boyfriend, Matthew Guerra, a capital murder case. The adults were shot and killed.

title: Shakira’s hometown unveils a giant statue of the beloved Colombian pop star
description: The mayor of Barranquilla and the pop star's parents appeared at an event to unveil a six meter statue which depicts Shakira in a belly dancing outfit, along the banks of the Magdalena River.
